            "id": 5943235,
            "title": "盤中速報 - CVS保健(CVS-US)大跌5.03%，報65.1美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>CVS保健(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CVS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CVS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CVS-US</a>)截至台北時間17日21:33股價下跌3.45美元，報65.10美元，跌幅5.03%，成交量1,805,885（股），盤中最高價66.65美元、最低價65.04美元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-1.22%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.2%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.25%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.3%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>CVS保健(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CVS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CVS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CVS-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+1.36%</li> <li>近 1 月：+4.37%</li> <li>近 3 月：+31.93%</li> <li>近 6 月：+5.43%</li> <li>今年以來：+52.71%</li></ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/5943235",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-17 21:48:20",
